text:
-2015.04 등록 /무사고 단순교환/미사노 레드/1만키로 리스승계 인수 2대차주
-420마력 55토크 / 0-100 3.8S 셋팅
-2014 CLUB SPORT QUATTRO CONCEPT + WIDE BODY KIT World 1 of 1
(원바디로 작업하는데 굉장한 노력과 비용 소요)
-R8 4S FRONT BUCKET SEAT + RS3 REAR LIMITED SEAT
(신형 R8 레카로 순정버킷시트에 AUDI SPORT LED 개발 제작 + 한정 알칸타라 순정 RS3 리어시트)
-2022~23 현행 VIRTUAL COCKPIT RETROFIT + MMI SYSTEM + 2023 RS3 MONITOR ADD ON
(COCKPIT의 모든 기능을 ADD ON 한상태로 전장작업의 집대성)
-AUDI ORIGINAL HUD
(ORIGINAL ACCESSORY HEAD UP DISPLAY)
-SIDE ASSIST + REAL CARBON MIRRO COVER
(후측방 경보 LED + BMW 'M' TYPE REAR CARBON MIRROR 제작)
-ELECTRIC AUTO SPOILER
(CLUBSPORT QUATTRO CONCEPT / AUDI 순정타입으로 버튼 동작과 GPS 속도감응 동작 둘다 가능
-실내 FULL ALCANTARA 정품 랩핑 및 AUDI ORIGINAL BLACK PILLA PART
(일반 스웨이드가 아닌 이태리 정품 알칸타라 / 아우디 순정 블랙 필러)
-실내 외 REAL CARBON PART
(수전사,랩핑 같은 격 떨어지는거 젤 혐오하는사람. 순정 RS3 파츠 외에 도어캐치, 도어핸들 등 리얼카본)
-ENGINE HOOD GLASS / REAL CARBON 및 ACCESSORY
(엔진,브레이크오일,ECU,배터리커버,흡기시스템 풀카본
-NORMAL HEATED STEERING WHEEL
-RS SAFETY BELT
(카피제품 아닌 순정 BELT ASS' 교체)
-R8/HURACAN STEEL BRAKE SYSTEM
(앞 8PISTON, 뒤 4PISTON / 정품파츠들로 이뤄져있으며 셋팅을 위한 부자재에만 수백만원 소요)

-Registered in 2015.04 / Accident-free simple exchange / Misano Red / 10,000 km lease succession acquisition 2nd borrower
-420 horsepower 55 torque / 0-100 3.8S setting
-2014 CLUB SPORT QUATTRO CONCEPT + WIDE BODY KIT World 1 of 1
(It takes a lot of effort and cost to work with one body)
-R8 4S FRONT BUCKET SEAT + RS3 REAR LIMITED SEAT
(Development and production of AUDI SPORT LED on new R8 Recaro genuine bucket seat + Limited Alcantara genuine RS3 rear seat)
-2022~23 Current VIRTUAL COCKPIT RETROFIT + MMI SYSTEM + 2023 RS3 MONITOR ADD ON
(Collective of battlefield work with all functions of COKPIT ADD ON)
-AUDI ORIGINAL HUD
(ORIGINAL ACCESSORY HEAD UP DISPLAY)
-SIDE ASSIST + REAL CARBON MIRRO COVER
(Rear Alert LED + BMW 'M' TYPE REAR CARBON MIRROR Produced)
-ELECTRIC AUTO SPOILER
(CLUBSPORT QUATTRO CONCEPT / AUDI genuine type, capable of both button operation and GPS speed response operation
-Indoor FULL ALCANTARA Genuine Wrapping and AUDI ORIGINAL BLACK PILLA PART
(Italian genuine Alcantara, not regular suede / Audi genuine black filler)
-Indoor and outdoor REAL CARBON PART
(People who hate inferior things like water transfer and wrapping. In addition to genuine RS3 parts, real carbon such as door catches and door handles)
-ENGINE HOOD GLASS / REAL CARBON and ACCESSORY
(Engine, brake oil, ECU, battery cover, intake system full carbon)
-NORMAL HEATED STEERING WHEEL
-RS SAFETY BELT
(Replacement with ‘genuine BELT ASS’, not a copy product)
-R8/HURACAN STEEL BRAKE SYSTEM
(8 PISTON in the front, 4 PISTON in the rear / Consists of genuine parts, Costs millions of won only for subsidiary materials for setting)
